00:44:30,000 --> 00:44:30,894
Lahat kayo.

759
00:44:30,918 --> 00:44:32,561
Pero ang lahat ay sadyang magulo.

760
00:44:32,585 --> 00:44:33,355
Ang daming nangyari.

761
00:44:33,379 --> 00:44:35,297
Hinanap ko lang ang tamang timing.

762
00:44:35,547 --> 00:44:36,798
Pasensya na talaga, Moo.

763
00:44:36,923 --> 00:44:38,091
Pasensya na, Moo.

764
00:44:38,258 --> 00:44:39,509
Pasensya na.

765
00:44:42,117 --> 00:44:43,409
Ayos lang 'yan, Moo.

766
00:44:44,222 --> 00:44:45,557
Huwag mo nang isipin pa 'yan.

767
00:44:49,060 --> 00:44:50,103
Pero pangako ko.

768
00:44:50,353 --> 00:44:51,353
Pangako talaga.

769
00:44:51,604 --> 00:44:53,606
Ikaw ang unang
makakaalam ng mga sikreto ko ngayon.

770
00:44:53,982 --> 00:44:54,834
Hindi na Cuz.

771
00:44:54,858 --> 00:44:55,858
Gagawin mo.

772
00:44:57,902 --> 00:44:58,587
Sige.

773
00:44:58,611 --> 00:44:59,611
Sige, sige.

774
00:45:00,030 --> 00:45:01,030
Saan...

775
00:45:04,826 --> 00:45:05,826
Ano ito?

776
00:45:05,869 --> 00:45:07,412
Paano kung nalaman mo na...

777
00:45:08,038 --> 00:45:10,040
Masamang tao ba talaga si Roswell?

778
00:45:11,750 --> 00:45:12,750
Ha?

779
00:45:13,501 --> 00:45:14,544
Isang masamang tao?

780
00:45:14,753 --> 00:45:16,796
Hindi masamang tao si Zeke, Moo.

781
00:45:18,840 --> 00:45:20,359
Pero noong una ko siyang nakilala,

782
00:45:20,383 --> 00:45:22,093
Akala ko rin talaga masamang tao siya.

783
00:45:22,385 --> 00:45:23,278
Dahil diba?

784
00:45:23,303 --> 00:45:23,989
Lagi siyang galit.

785
00:45:24,013 --> 00:45:25,823
Palagi siyang nakakunot ang noo.

786
00:45:25,847 --> 00:45:27,515
Laging nakakunot ang mga kilay niya.

787
00:45:27,724 --> 00:45:30,352
At hindi talaga siya
yung tipo na makikipagbati sa mga tao.

788
00:45:30,894 --> 00:45:32,854
Pero alam mo ba,
Moo? Habang lumilipas ang panahon,

789
00:45:33,313 --> 00:45:35,732
Nakita ko na
mabuting tao pala talaga si Zeke.

790
00:45:38,818 --> 00:45:39,818
Mabuti?

791
00:45:42,322 --> 00:45:45,700
Paano kung malaman mong
kaya niyang pumatay ng tao?

792
00:45:52,248 --> 00:45:54,042
Hinanap kita kung saan-saan.

793
00:45:57,545 --> 00:45:58,546
Zeke! Nabaril ako!

794
00:45:58,630 --> 00:46:00,215
Ito ba talaga ang katotohanan?

795
00:46:03,218 --> 00:46:04,612
Pinahanga mo ako, Young.

796
00:46:04,636 --> 00:46:05,612
Hindi ka pa tapos.

797
00:46:05,637 --> 00:46:08,074
Kailangan mong pumatay ng tatlong tao.

798
00:46:08,098 --> 00:46:12,535
Sa ngayon, ang
kita ng kumpanya ay bumaba ng 20%

799
00:46:12,560 --> 00:46:14,979
at 10% sa buong korporasyon.

800
00:46:15,021 --> 00:46:18,274
May kung ano...
may maliit na aberya lang

801
00:46:18,525 --> 00:46:19,734
sa kompanya.

802
00:46:21,650 --> 00:46:22,650
Ha?

803
00:46:22,675 --> 00:46:23,675
Uy, Aeimie.

804
00:46:28,824 --> 00:46:30,325
Sasabihin ko sa board

805
00:46:30,350 --> 00:46:31,850
lahat ng iniisip ko ngayon

806
00:46:31,913 --> 00:46:34,666
yung text message niya!

807
00:46:35,166 --> 00:46:37,168
Malaking halaga ng pera ang nawawala?

808
00:46:37,502 --> 00:46:38,438
Sigurado ako

809
00:46:38,462 --> 00:46:40,213
sila ang dapat sisihin.

810
00:46:40,672 --> 00:46:41,672
Mama!

811
00:46:41,996 --> 00:46:42,996
Maayos ba ang pakiramdam mo?

812
00:46:43,258 --> 00:46:46,237
Ginoong Blood, si Ginang Roswell ay
nasa loob na ng opisina.

813
00:46:46,261 --> 00:46:47,262
Maaari ka nang pumasok.
